GG Troje
========

Map by FireWavezZ
-------------

### Models by Gmaps

Troje (Troy) was a city, both factual and legendary, located in northwest Anatolia in what is now Turkey. It is best known for being the setting of the Trojan War and the wooden artifact the Trojan horse.

The map has 32 spawn points. Thanks to Gmaps for making these never seen models for my map!

Have fun!
